--[[
 This script creates a draggable GUI for viewing, copying, blacklisting, and whitelisting remote calls.
 Each remote invocation displays:
   - The remote type (RemoteEvent or RemoteFunction)
   - The full object path in the game hierarchy
   - Its arguments, including nested tables
 Blacklisted requests are prevented from appearing in the logs and can be later whitelisted again.

 New Features:
   - Sizable scrolling frames for large amounts of remote calls and for large argument details.
   - "Resend request" button to re-invoke the remote with editable arguments (response printed to the console).
]]

